  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The Rheumatoid Arthritis DMARD Intervention and Utilization Study (RADIUS 1) is designed to
      systematically collect and document use patterns, effectiveness, and safety of DMARD
      treatments currently used in the management of rheumatoid arthritis (RA). It is anticipated
      that study data may help improve the quality of information upon which clinical decisions are
      based.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
